'''罗兰岗殴打事件'''是2015年4月在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[罗兰岗|罗兰岗]]发生的两起中国留学生欺凌、袭击事件。

共六名中国籍留学生参与殴打了两位中国女孩。在袭击者中，杨玉涵（{{lang|en|Coco Yang}}）、章鑫磊（{{lang|en|John Zhang}}）和翟芸瑶（{{lang|en|Helen Zhai}}）已成年<ref>Chang, Cindy. "[http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-parachute-kids-sentencing-20160217-story.html Sentenced to prison for assault, teenage 'parachute kids' deliver warning to adults in China] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6fOlSk6aY?url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-parachute-kids-sentencing-20160217-story.html |date=20160218221200 |dateformat=iso }}" (). ''[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]''. February 17, 2016. Retrieved on February 18, 2016.</ref><ref>"[http://www.sgvtribune.com/general-news/20160217/chinese-teens-sentenced-in-brutal-rowland-heights-beatings Chinese teens sentenced in brutal Rowland Heights beatings] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6fRV88OZk?url=http://www.sgvtribune.com/general-news/20160217/chinese-teens-sentenced-in-brutal-rowland-heights-beatings |date=20160220172239 |dateformat=iso }}" (). Ruby Gonzales, ''[[San_Gabriel_Valley_Tribune|San Gabriel Valley Tribune]]''. February 17, 2016. retrieved 2/19/16.</ref>，其余三名为未成年人。三名成年犯案者已在2015年3月31日被执法部门逮捕。<ref name=LACountygov>"[http://da.lacounty.gov/media/news/three-chinese-nationals-sentenced-prison-kidnapping-assaults-rowland-heights February 17, 2016: Three Chinese Nationals Sentenced to Prison for Kidnapping, Assaults in Rowland Heights] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6fPFiJvDh?url=http://da.lacounty.gov/media/news/three-chinese-nationals-sentenced-prison-kidnapping-assaults-rowland-heights |date=20160219055355 |dateformat=iso }}" (). Los Angeles County. Retrieved on February 18, 2016.</ref> 三人的[[保释金|保释金]]均被设定为300万美元。<ref>Xie, Jun. "[http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/926811.shtml Overseas students on trial for torture ] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6fOkgXis3?url=http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/926811.shtml |date=20160218220008 |dateformat=iso }}" (). ''[[Global_Times|Global Times]]''. June 13, 2015. Retrieved on February 18, 2016.</ref> 其中一名案犯的父亲因为贿赂证人而被捕。<ref name=Niuyue>Niu, Yue. "[http://usa.chinadaily.com.cn/epaper/2015-06/15/content_21005464.htm Chinese students on trial in alleged torture of peer] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6fOjJgQTP?url=http://web.archive.org/web/20160218212031/http://usa.chinadaily.com.cn/epaper/2015-06/15/content_21005464.htm |date=20160218213914 |dateformat=iso }}" (). ''[[China_Daily|China Daily]]''. June 15, 2015. page 2. Retrieved on February 18, 2016.</ref>

三名嫌犯被控[[虐待|虐待]]与绑架罪。在加州虐待罪最高可被判处[[终身监禁|终身监禁]]。所有涉案人员均被判入狱服刑。翟芸瑶被判有期徒刑13年，杨玉涵被判10年，章鑫磊被判6年。<ref>Chang, Cindy. "[http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-parachute-kids-sentencing-20160217-story.html Sentenced to prison for assault, teenage 'parachute kids' deliver warning to adults in China]" ([https://www.webcitation.org/6fOlSk6aY?url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-parachute-kids-sentencing-20160217-story.html Archive]). ''[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]''. February 17, 2016. Retrieved on February 18, 2016.</ref>

